title: Castro Valley Cars
name: Castro Valley Cars
description:
We provide one of the best selections of used and new cars. Our top rated auto service department provides service for the Castro Valley community.

At Castro Valley Cars, our number one concern is your satisfaction! We pride ourselves on outstanding customer service and convenience. We strive to make our service experience as pleasant as possible by staffing our department with friendly and capable personnel. Our belief that if we listen closely to your individual needs and concerns we can ensure that the correct repairs and maintenance can be offered and completed quickly and accurately. We keep our prices competitive by shopping around so that you won't have to. We invite you to take advantage of our current service specials and pay us a visit soon!
